MS Gothic', sans-serief; background-color: rgb(88, 188, 134); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px;\">\n\t\t<b>课程详情</b></p>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">宽学网 自我管理精品课</span></strong><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">原价：<strike>180</strike></strong>元<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span><br />\n\t<span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 51);\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">沪江团购价：59元！</span></strong></span></span><br />\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">课时数：20</strong>课时<br />\n\t<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有效期：90</strong>天</span></span><br />\n\t<span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">适用人群：</strong></span><br />\n\t<span>1. 初入职场，希望快速融入团队的学员</span><br />\n\t<span>2. 想要提升工作效率的学员</span><br />\n\t<span>3. 工作压力大，需要调整职场心态的学员</span><br />\n\t<span>4. 想要提高语言沟通能力和谈判技巧的学员</span><br />\n\t<span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">学习目标：</strong></span><br />\n\t<span>1. 掌握人际沟通的能力，提高说服力</span><br />\n\t<span>2. 掌握合理分配时间与高效执行的能力</span><br />\n\t<span>3. 掌握抗压技巧，调整良好心态</span><br />\n\t<span>4. 掌握谈判、记录、会议的技能</span><br />\n\t<span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">课程表：</strong></span><br />\n\t<a href=\"http://tuan.hujiang.com/tuangou/p915/?source=499\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/bef96b90-bf9a-48dc-b9bd-38f97c7a2084_01.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 6px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, SimSun, Arial, 'Arial Unicode MS', MingLiu, PMingLiu, 'MS Gothic', sans-serief; background-color: rgb(88, 188, 134); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; bo